mem_center_iff:
@[to_additive]
theorem mem_center_iff {z : M} : z ∈ center M ↔ ∀ g, g * z = z * g :=
  iff.rfl
#align mem_center_iff mem_center_iff

@[to_additive]
theorem coe_center : ↑(center M) = Set.center M :=
  rfl
#align coe_center coe_center
center_to_subsemigroup:
@[simp]
theorem center_to_subsemigroup : (center M).to_subsemigroup = Subsemigroup.center M :=
  rfl
#align center_to_subsemigroup center_to_subsemigroup
center_to_add_subsemigroup:
theorem _root_.add_submonoid.center_to_add_subsemigroup (M) [AddMonoid M] :
    (AddSubmonoid.center M).to_add_subsemigroup = AddSubsemigroup.center M :=
  rfl
#align add_submonoid.center_to_add_subsemigroup add_submonoid.center_to_add_subsemigroup
center_eq_top:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr⊤» -/
@[simp]
theorem center_eq_top : center M = «expr⊤» :=
  SetLike.coe_injective (Set.center_eq_univ M)
#align center_eq_top center_eq_top
